Summary:	MySessions Firefox extension
Summary(ru_RU.UTF-8):	расширение MySessions для Firefox

License:	%mpl
Group:		Networking/WWW
URL:		https://addons.mozilla.org/firefox/addon/my-sessions/
BuildArch:      noarch

Source0:	%rname.xpi
